				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hi,
<br />

<br />
We installed it on a board with EasyMod that has a lot of mods and it was no problem at all.
<br />

<br />
I would suggest you install the advanced visual confirmation, which we also have, to prevent robotic registration.
<br />

<br />
In addition we also installed Anti-bot Guest Post Mod by Oliver Tseng -&gt; http: / / debatingchristianity [dot] com (sorry, this forum has bbAntiSpam, cant post links <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="Wink" border="0" /> ). This mod adds a Yes/No pulldown and needs to be manually set to Yes before a guest can post. This prevents bots posting (although I have noticed some bots can do this automatically.
<br />

<br />
Good luck killing the spammers <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
